articles.contents:
About Me
Hello, this is the short description of my self as recommended by the data science course I am taking right now, my name is Stefan.
About the Project
The Time Hass Come | An introspective look at the avocado trends of the United States
Goals
Analyse the fluctuation of sale volumes across all U.S. states
Link these fluctuations to known influencers of sale volumes
These may be difficult to identify and will probably be scrapped, but what can you do?

Visualize the relationship between price and sale volume fluctuations
“This is data science”
Preceptor

Kane’s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp
